Description:
UNDER CONTRACT/ UNDER OFFER
CRANBOURNE EAST:If you are looking to buy a great family home in a great location then 12 Carnavon Street needs to be seen to be appreciated!
With a functional, free flowing floor plan the property itself features 4 generous bedrooms. The master offers a WIR and a FES. The balance of the bedrooms all have BIR and beds 3 and 4 nearby to the family bathroom with separate bath and shower facilities.
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and is finished with a good amount of cupboard space, island bench tops, tiled splash back, S/S appliances including oven, gas cook top, rangehood and dishwasher.
Take advantage of the 3 living zones making year-round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good movie or a book with the front living area, carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in the family zone or grab a seat around the kitchen table with the family in the dining area.
Added internal extras are gas ducted heating, evap cooling, a mix of tiles and carpet and neutral tones throughout.
Step outside and be greeted by a sensational street scape offering a modern facade and landscaping. A wide lengthy concrete driveway leads to the remote double garage. There is internal access to the house and single door to the side of the house. The backyard is perfect for the entire family and pets. The entertaining aspect is completed with an underroof alfresco that is fit for all year round use.
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
Don't waste your time with a frustrating building process! It's all here waiting for you and you don't even need to lift a finger!
*PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*!

Versatile Floorplan & Everything at Your Doorstep!!
An inviting abode on a land size of approx. 545sqm makes this the perfect family home. Located in the desirable Hunt Club, this versatile home showcases 3 bedrooms plus study, or theatre room or 3rd living area or 4th bedroom!!…. The choice is yours! With innovation and quality seamlessly integrated throughout this home you can look forward to moving straight in and do nothing but enjoy. A large kitchen with an expansive island bench, marvellous for cooking and entertaining. The dining area leads to the undercover outdoor alfresco with BBQ that is perfectly set up for family gatherings all year round. To the rear of the home you will discover the spacious yet cosy living area to relax and watch the latest on Netflix. Cleverly thought out design, chic master bedroom with lavishly styled ensuite & walk in robe. Two/three further extra sizeable bedrooms all with BIRs. A feast of extras include sun-soaked private backyard space, elegant light-fittings, nine solar panels, heating & cooling and double remote garage to name a few. Situated remarkably close to the main hub, makes travelling easy yet still enjoy the benefits of a quiet, tranquil environment.
Just steps from The Hunt Club shopping centre & only moments from Cranbourne East primary school, Casey Grammar, childcare centres & public transport options. Just a few steps from the park, scenic walking tracks and public transportation - all adding to the recreational and family lifestyle benefits available here. Take this rare opportunity to inspect a magnificent home offering timeless quality. Be quick to avoid disappointment!

Description:
A PRISTINE SINGLE OWNER HOME IN A PERFECT COURT STYLE POSITION - 3 BEDROOMS + STUDY!
HUNT CLUB ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST: After some 17 years and many happy memories it's time for the current owners of this immaculate family home to move on. Loved and cared for over the journey, they are leaving behind a near perfect opportunity for first time buyers, investors and retirees to take advantage of!
As one of the very first properties built in this tightly held estate, 27 Masterton Place rests in a tree lined court-like location with a park/wetlands at one end and the Hunt Club shopping centre at the other! In stunning display condition, the property itself rests on a low maintenance block with a timeless facade fronted by a double remote garage and covered front porch.
Step inside and be greeted by dual living zones including a formal lounge plus an open plan family/meals area. The pristine hostess kitchen is complete with a large corner pantry, breakfast bar and quality appliances.
There are 3 robed bedrooms, including the master with its own walk in wardrobe and a full ensuite this is complemented by the family bathroom and second toilet. In addition, there's also a dedicated study, ducted heating, split system air-conditioning, multiple ceiling fans, ducted vacuuming, intercom system and a security alarm for added peace of mind! Not to mention the 12 x 250W solar panels with a 3.5W inverter, a great addition offering you the potential to save on your energy bills!
With a generous parcel of land measuring app. 480m2 there is a spacious grass free backyard with a huge 12m (app.) long pergola ideal for year round entertaining. Not to mention the handy garden shed for added storage facilities!
Within close proximity to picturesque wetlands and walking/bike paths the Hunt Club is a multi-award winning estate offering a complete range of education facilities including a childcare centre, Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College. Buses weave through the estate whilst the recently opened Hunt Club Village has an array of shopping options. Don't forget the future plans for a Cranbourne East railway station!
Centrally located to freeways and public transport enroute to the Melbourne CBD the location is second to none! For those of you who like to stay closer to home it's only a brisk drive to the Cranbourne Park shopping centre, Berwick Village, Fountain Gate shopping centre, Casey Lifestyle centre and the Casey Fields sporting complex. Within close vicinity to an array of further Primary, Secondary and Tertiary institutions, the entire family has easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation!

Description:
**UNDER OFFER / UNDER CONTRACT**
MAYFIELD ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST: Literally brand new, brilliantly designed and finished to a standard far beyond what many buyers would expect, this prestige home is positioned in the flourishing Mayfield Estate and stands a head and shoulders above the competition. The modern facade further emphasises its architectural edge and gives an instant street appeal begging you to step inside!
Upon entry you are greeted by hard wearing timber look flooring, light paint tones and extras including LED lighting, high ceilings, ornate cornices and feature doors which all add to the overall appeal.
From the entry hall you walk past the study, fitted with 2 built in desks, and head towards the open plan living/dining area complete with a bonus powder room. The galley style hostess kitchen is one of the main selling points and is complete with stone benches, stainless appliances, a mirrored glass splash back and walk in pantry.
Step upstairs to find an additional living zone with a luxurious gas log fireplace, 4 genuine robed bedrooms and 2 bathrooms including a full ensuite. There is plenty of room for any large or growing family!
Don't forget the host of bonuses including ducted reverse cycle heating/refrigerated cooling, a double remote garage with internal access/storage facilities and a North facing courtyard that is grass free for easy maintenance.
In an estate lined with parks and playgrounds you are within a short drive to freeway access and all of the amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. You are also only minutes away from the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Indoor Sports Centre! With additional shopping precincts in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club local amenities are always going to be close by, whilst the recently revamped Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre offers an abundance of cafes and restaurants. Don't forget the proposed Cranbourne East train station and the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!
This is the perfect opportunity for first timers looking to break into the market, empty nesters and those looking to invest in one of the most popular estates in Cranbourne East!
If you want your family to have easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation then call before it's SELLING, SELLING ..... SOLD!

Description:
Huge Simonds family home on 615m2
This attractive five bedroom home is in a brilliant location and offers plenty of quality features which are sure to impress. Being a Simonds built home with all the upgrades, this is one worth adding to your viewing list!
Features include:
- Feature entrance with landscaped gardens and decked portico
- Huge Master bedroom with generous walk in robe, plantation shutters and ensuite including large shower and separate toilet
- Four more generous bedrooms - three with built in robes and the last being a 5th bedroom/study or extra lounge
- Beautiful central kitchen with plenty of inclusions - 900mm gas cooktop, dishwasher, breakfast bar, stone benches, walk in pantry, plumbed fridge area and plenty of cupboard space
- Flexible living space- a big open plan living area as well as separate theater room for movie enthusiasts
- HUGE undercover alfresco area with stacks of extras such as decking, an outdoor heater plus a built in bar and seating- perfect for entertaining all year round
- Remote double garage with access door through as well as internal access to the home
- For the caravan or boat enthusiast you have secure side access on both sides of the home
- Extras include: Ducted heating, two split system A/C units, downlights throughout plus loads more!
Set conveniently on a 615m2 block in the heart of the popular Cascades on Clyde, all this is within walking distance to local parklands and bus services, easy access to schools such as Cranbourne East Secondary College and a short drive to Selandra Rise Shopping Center. The perfect choice for those looking for a quality family home in a well sought after location!

Description:
ALMOST BRAND NEW WITH NOTHING TO BE DONE JUST MOVE IN!!
CRANBOURNE EAST (Livingston Estate):Live a lifestyle of luxury and comfort in this beautiful home. Built in 2017 and barely a year old, you will no doubt fall in love as soon as you walk through the front door.
Comprising of 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, double car garage and open plan living, there is plenty of space for any family. The wide entry compliments the spaciousness throughout the house, complete with a large living area and added storage space. The master bedroom has a full en-suite, twin vanities, Caesar stone benches and walk in robe. You will not be disappointed with the splendour and functionality of the kitchen, with Caesar stone bench tops, glass splashback, walk in pantry and dishwasher.
If entertaining friends and family is something you love to do, then you will be spoilt for choice! The open plan living area is complimented by a Theatre room where you can enjoy your favourite T.V show or movie, while enjoying a well deserved break. Or why not have the kids' friends over for a movie night, while you relax and unwind in the Alfresco area? Complete with fully landscaped gardens, you will love sitting outside on those glorious summer days, taking in the beauty of your surrounds.
Situated in the established Cranbourne East pocket, all local amenities are within a short distance of the home.
Summary of internal and external features include:
- Approx. 448 sqm land & Built in 2017
- Two separate living zones - open plan living and Theatre room
- Plenty of natural light all day
- Crim safe door to all entry points
- Master with full en suite with WIR
- Ducted heating
- Evaporative cooling
- High ceiling
- Glass Splash Back
- Caesar stone bench tops: kitchen and bathrooms
- 900 mm oven
- 900 mm gas cook top
- Spacious walk in pantry
- Dishwasher
- Overhead cupboards in the kitchen
- LED down lights
- Quality carpets and flooring
- Stainless steel range hood
- Solar hot water system
- Remote controlled double lock up garage
- Alarm system
- Security cameras
- Sliding doors in to Alfresco
- Internal and external access from the garage
- Fully secure and landscaped backyard
This property is situated within close proximity to Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College, as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby, is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Library which is just across the road. Adding to the attraction of this home is a proposed primary school just 250m away.
*** PLEASE NOTE: As this house is almost brand new the direction guides on navigations may not show up, hence please follow the below directions:
From Berwick Cranbourne Road (C407) - Eliburn Drive - Take a right to Bankton Avenue - Take a left to Newington Drive - Parkhurst Drive - Tinnadice Road (Second right from Parkhurst Drive) ***

Description:
SOLD BY MATTHEW RINGERI
CRANBOURNE EAST-HUNT CLUB: If you are looking to buy a great family home in a rare court location then 6 Chief Court needs to be seen to be appreciated!
Constructed by well known builders Porter Davis this complete package measures some 32sq underroof and it sits proudly on a massive app. 716m2 block!
With a functional, free flowing floor plan the property itself features 4 generous bedrooms plus an open study. The master offers a WIR and a FES providing shower, dual vanities complete with stone bench top and feature wall tiling. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4, all with built in robes, ceiling fans and are near the family bathroom with separate bath and shower facilities.
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and is finished with huge amounts of cupboard space, stone bench tops, glass splash back, quality appliances including 900mm free standing oven with 5-burner hot plate, rangehood plus stainless steel dishwasher, island bench and wide fridge cavity. The walk-in pantry completes this already fantastic kitchen.
Take advantage of the 3 separate living zones making year-round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good movie with the front theatre room, carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in the family zone or relax with the kids rear rumpus.
Added internal extras include downlights, ducted heating, quality floor coverings and neutral colour tones throughout
Step outside and be greeted by a sensational street scape offering a modern facade and landscaping. A lengthy concrete driveway leads to the remote double garage. There is internal access to the house and single door to the side of the house. The backyard has opportunity written all over it. There is a blank canvas for you to make the dream backyard that you have always dreamt of. The entertaining aspect is completed with an underroof alfresco with 2 lots of sliding doors to access the kitchen and rumpus room. For all those with extra cars, boats, caravans, work equipment the option to install some side gates and have access to the backyard, with an option for a extra garage to be built (S.T.C.A).
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
Don't waste your time with a frustrating building process! It's all here waiting for you and you don't even need to lift a finger!
